    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 987.1 Cayman S features the high-revving 3.4L M97 flat-six, delivering linear power through a precise 6-speed manual transaxle. The mid-engine chassis balance is optimized with PASM (Porsche Active Suspension Management) and an upgraded short-shift kit for tactile engagement. Recent mechanical vetting includes a clean borescope inspection and a high-flow AOS installation to ensure long-term reliability. Riding on Michelin Pilot Sport 4S tires, the car exhibits exceptional lateral grip and communicative steering. A mechanically robust specimen with a documented service history, ready for spirited canyon runs.",
