      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a reliable, well-cared-for daily driver that still turns heads. The exterior paint retains a beautiful shine, showing only the minor stone chips and light surface marks consistent with careful, regular use. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and has been a smoke-free environment; the seats are free of tears, and the dashboard remains crack-free with all electronic features\u2014including the infotainment system and climate control\u2014operating perfectly. Under the hood, the engine is clean and runs quietly, benefiting from a documented history of on-time oil changes and preventative maintenance. The tires have plenty of tread remaining, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. It drives straight and true, offering a smooth ride that feels tight and responsive. This car is truly ready for the road with no immediate work required.",
